---
import BaseHead from '../components/BaseHead.astro';
import Header from '../components/Header.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import { Image } from 'astro:assets';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
	<head>
		<BaseHead title="Meet Juliette Stephens" description="Meet Juliette Stephens - Expert woodworker and creator of unique, handcrafted pieces" />
		<style>
			/* Import Matter TRIAL font */
			@import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Matter+TRIAL:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap');
			
			/* Apply Matter TRIAL font to all text */
			body, h1, h2, h3, h4, h5, h6, p, a, button, input, textarea, label {
				font-family: "Matter TRIAL", sans-serif !important;
			}
			
					main {
			width: 100%;
			max-width: 1200px;
			margin: 0 auto;
			padding: 2em;
			overflow-x: hidden;
			box-sizing: border-box;
		}
			
			.about-header {
				display: grid;
				grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
				gap: 2rem;
				align-items: center;
				margin-bottom: 3rem;
				padding: 2rem 0;
			}
			
			.profile-image {
				width: 600px;
				height: auto;
				flex-shrink: 0;
				overflow: hidden;
				box-sizing: border-box;
			}
			
			.profile-image img {
				width: 100%;
				height: 60vh;
				object-fit: cover;
				object-position: top center;
				display: block;
			}
			
			.title-section h1 {
				margin: 0 0 1rem 0;
				font-size: 2.5rem;
				color: rgb(var(--black));
				line-height: 1.2;
			}
			
			.title-section p {
				margin: 0;
				font-size: 1.2rem;
				color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
				line-height: 1.6;
			}
			
			.prose {
				color: rgb(var(--gray-dark));
				line-height: 1.7;
			}
			
			.prose p {
				margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
				font-size: 1.1rem;
			}
			
			@media (max-width: 768px) {
				.about-header {
					grid-template-columns: 1fr;
					text-align: center;
					gap: 1.5rem;
				}
				
				.profile-image {
					width: 100%;
					max-width: calc(100vw - 4em);
					height: auto;
					margin: 0 auto;
					overflow: hidden;
					box-sizing: border-box;
				}
				
				.profile-image img {
					object-position: top center;
					object-fit: cover;
					height: 30vh;
				}
				
				.title-section h1 {
					font-size: 2rem;
				}
				
				.title-section p {
					font-size: 1.1rem;
				}
			}
		</style>
	</head>
	<body>
		<Header />
		<main>
			<article>
				<div class="about-header">
					<div class="profile-image">
						<Image src="/juliette_salute.png" alt="Juliette Stephens" width={600} height={600} />
					</div>
					<div class="title-section">
						<h1>Meet Juliette Stephens</h1>
						<p>Expert woodworker and creator of unique, handcrafted pieces</p>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="prose">
					<p>
						Juliette Stephens is an expert woodworker with a passion for creating beautiful, functional pieces that blend traditional craftsmanship with modern design. Her work reflects a deep understanding of wood as a material and a commitment to quality that ensures each piece will last for generations.
					</p>

					<p>
						With years of experience in the craft, Juliette has developed a unique style that honors the natural beauty of wood while creating pieces that fit seamlessly into contemporary homes. Her attention to detail and dedication to sustainable practices make her work stand out in the world of custom woodworking.
					</p>

					<p>
						From custom furniture to decorative items, Juliette approaches each project with creativity and precision. She believes that every piece of wood has a story to tell, and her work helps bring those stories to life in homes and spaces where they can be appreciated and enjoyed.
					</p>

					<p>
						Whether you're looking for a statement piece for your home or a custom solution for a specific need, Juliette's expertise and artistic vision ensure that the final result will exceed your expectations. Her commitment to quality craftsmanship and personalized service makes her the ideal partner for bringing your woodworking dreams to reality.
					</p>
				</div>
			</article>
		</main>
		<Footer />
	</body>
</html>
